300
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:29,680
I'm sorry if he hurt you.

301
00:19:29,690 --> 00:19:32,990
But it's different
with me and ramon.

302
00:19:35,450 --> 00:19:37,660
So... I don't need your warning.

303
00:19:38,210 --> 00:19:40,410
You look like my dead ma.

304
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,990
He say that to you?

305
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,570
Next he'll ask for
a key to your place.

306
00:19:44,580 --> 00:19:47,820
Stuff will disappear.

307
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:50,320
He'll borrow your car.
It'll get stolen.

308
00:19:52,210 --> 00:19:54,150
What's going on?

309
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,840
She knows ramon.

310
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:58,740
You got to have hope.

311
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:01,020
Just because we ain't
morgan fairchild,

312
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:03,240
doesn't mean we don't
deserve somebody nice.

313
00:20:03,830 --> 00:20:05,910
Martha,who is this?

314
00:20:09,450 --> 00:20:12,060
We got to go home.

315
00:20:12,070 --> 00:20:14,890
Poor martha. I've been there.

316
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:18,150
One day you're on vacation
in denial city,

317
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:21,500
next day you're in a prison
of your own stupidity.

318
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:27,330
Thanks,eugenia.

319
00:20:27,810 --> 00:20:29,550
Well,stephanie,the roommate
lied about martha and ramon.

320
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:31,930
Said they didn't follow up.

321
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:34,790
Well,this guy was a
svengali with the ladies.

322
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:39,230
Maybe stephanie fell
for his schtick,too?

323
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,570
Oh,please. Protect ramon?

324
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:44,240
I couldn't stand him.

325
00:20:45,010 --> 00:20:47,820
Oh,you think you can just pick
and choose what you tell us?

326
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,230
I have a reputation you know.

327
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:53,820
As what?

328
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:55,770
The kind of men I date
have money,and prestige,

329
00:20:55,930 --> 00:20:58,660
and they do background checks.

330
