If they found out that
I lived with a thief,

331
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:05,370
all this... means nothing.

332
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:09,540
Thief. Oh,you mean ramon?

333
00:21:12,130 --> 00:21:15,700
Martha?

334
00:21:15,950 --> 00:21:18,420
look,martha was your roommate.

335
00:21:18,430 --> 00:21:21,740
Doesn't mean she reflects on you.

336
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:23,640
I can tell you're... classy.

337
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:27,330
True.

338
00:21:27,340 --> 00:21:28,840
So you can imagine how I felt.

339
00:21:28,850 --> 00:21:32,570
About what?

340
00:21:32,580 --> 00:21:38,070
The day that lady with the
braid saw us at the supermarket.

341
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:41,300
We raced home,and martha she just...

342
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:49,250
transformed.

343
00:21:50,870 --> 00:21:52,290
baby.

344
00:21:52,300 --> 00:21:56,790
This thing's out of whack. I was,uh,

345
00:21:57,270 --> 00:22:00,650
I was going to run it down to my buddy's shop
and get it fixed before murphy brown comes on.

346
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:12,590
Steph,will you give us a sec?

347
00:22:12,970 --> 00:22:17,590
