474
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:51,490
home sweet home.

475
00:29:52,350 --> 00:29:53,790
this is what we put
our down payment on?

476
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:56,190
You're kidding,right?

477
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:59,860
You have to use your
imagination,buella.

478
00:29:59,870 --> 00:30:02,270
I mean,it's not built yet,but,
oh,it's going to be beautiful.

479
00:30:06,990 --> 00:30:08,700
You know what?
Here we go.

480
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:10,380
I just carried you
over the threshold.

481
00:30:10,390 --> 00:30:12,050
- You did?
- I did.

482
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:13,240
Close your eyes so
you can picture it.

483
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,230
- Okay.
- Okay?

484
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:17,320
- They closed?
- Yes.

485
00:30:17,910 --> 00:30:22,010
Yeah? There's the front door.

486
00:30:22,020 --> 00:30:23,620
There's the little stone path
leading up toward the fence.

487
00:30:23,630 --> 00:30:26,340
Little front yard.

488
00:30:26,350 --> 00:30:28,560
Seriously? Like with
bushes and stuff?

489
00:30:28,570 --> 00:30:30,550
Keep 'em closed.

490
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:33,910
- keep 'em closed.
- All right.

491
00:30:35,190 --> 00:30:37,050
Yes,with bushes and stuff.

492
00:30:56,100 --> 00:30:57,630
I love you.

493
00:30:58,410 --> 00:30:59,290
Oh,my god!

494
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:01,570
Martha... stop crying.

495
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:03,850
Martha,martha,stop crying.

496
00:31:03,930 --> 00:31:06,610
That was fantastic.

497
00:31:06,620 --> 00:31:08,060
You were freakin'
gorgeous just then.

498
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:10,410
Really?

499
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:21,350
This stuff becomes you,baby.

500
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:23,100
You sure that wasn't a vision
from your crack pipe,cherry?

501
00:31:23,110 --> 00:31:27,670
That's what happened.

502
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:34,980
Big girl's shakin' like a leaf,
but she took that other broad out.

503
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:36,930
come see my show at the
manhole tuesday night.

504
00:31:36,970 --> 00:31:39,760
It's slammin',girl.

505
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:43,790
And give choco-love my flyer.

506
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:50,760
sure. Thanks,cherry.

507
00:31:51,530 --> 00:31:52,710
For you... choco-love.

508
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:56,290
That was vera.

509
00:31:56,300 --> 00:31:58,940
Ran martha's alias,serena
montagne,and got a hit.

510
00:31:58,950 --> 00:32:01,670
