than marriage certificates?

511
00:32:01,990 --> 00:32:02,930
Turns out serena took out
a life insurance policy.

512
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:04,970
On who?

513
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:07,300
Ramon delgado.

514
00:32:07,310 --> 00:32:11,730
Guess martha got the
hang of the con game.

515
00:32:13,730 --> 00:32:16,030
Decided to step it up a notch,
take out her true love.

516
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:18,890
So martha tried to turn
the tables on ramon.

517
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:20,950
And scam the scammer.
Maybe he found out.

518
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,480
- And he took her out first.
- She was deep in the game.

519
00:32:22,490 --> 00:32:25,360
Her fake name--
serena montagne--

520
00:32:25,370 --> 00:32:26,820
she used it for a lot more than
the life insurance policy on ramon.

521
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:28,940
Credit cards.

522
00:32:28,950 --> 00:32:30,120
And a safe deposit box.

523
00:32:30,130 --> 00:32:31,660
And guess what was in it?

524
00:32:31,670 --> 00:32:32,440
Other half of the diary.

525
00:32:32,450 --> 00:32:36,460
What'd she give us?

526
00:32:36,470 --> 00:32:38,430
Writes about buella stiffler and the
four other women she and ramon murdered.

527
00:32:38,850 --> 00:32:41,000
Any insight into martha's murder?

528
00:32:41,010 --> 00:32:43,510
Nothing caught up with them
from their crime spree.

529
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:45,790
Except martha's conscience.

530
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:52,620
<i>dear love,</i>

531
00:32:53,710 --> 00:32:56,460
<i>may you keep track of every second
that we are together on this earth.</i>

532
00:32:57,100 --> 00:33:00,090
Your husband,edwin.

533
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:05,000
1947.

